com.thomsonreuters.upa.transport

Interface InProgInfo


  • public interface InProgInfo
    Information for the In Progress Connection State of Channel.init(InProgInfo, Error).
    If a backward compatibility reconnection occurs, the socket channel may change. This is how that information is relayed.
    See Also:
    InProgFlags, Channel
